scripts.version: git add . && git commit -am "chore: release v$npm_package_version"
scripts.postversion: git push && git push origin --tags && npm publish
scripts.release: npx unbuild && npm version patch && git add . && git commit -m "chore: release @oeos-components/utils v$(npm pkg get version | sed 's/"//g')" && git push && git push origin && npm publish
